
###  INSTALLING IMPORTANT PACKAGES

## FIRST WE WILL INSTALL, pip install gunicorn-- THIS IS ESSENTIALLY A WSGI HTTP SEVRER, WHICH IS GOING TO ALLOW US TO BRIDGE
## THE CONNECTION BETWEEN OUR DJANGO APPLICATION AND RENDER WEB SERVICES

## THEN WE INSTALL, pip install environ, which is going to allow us to create environment variables, which will go ahead
## and ensure that allof our sensitive data is kept secure, such as our access keys or data

